&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Altruist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Altruist is transforming the multi-trillion dollar wealth management industry by building an AI platform for wealth professionals. We partner with financial advisors nationwide, empowering them to grow, optimize time and resources, and deliver superior outcomes for their clients.&lt;/p&gt;
